1
00:00:13,010 --> 00:00:15,810
[Episode 25]

2
00:00:20,417 --> 00:00:21,376
At this point,

3
00:00:22,937 --> 00:00:24,536
do you have nothing to say to me?

4
00:00:32,977 --> 00:00:34,496
About Nanxi's pregnancy,

5
00:00:36,537 --> 00:00:37,856
I deliberately hid it from you.

6
00:00:39,497 --> 00:00:40,376
I used you.

7
00:00:41,217 --> 00:00:41,976
I hurt you.

8
00:00:44,057 --> 00:00:44,856
I'm sorry.

9
00:00:45,977 --> 00:00:47,216
I thought between us,

10
00:00:47,657 --> 00:00:48,856
there was enough trust.

11
00:00:49,537 --> 00:00:50,856
You'd consider me one of your own.

12
00:00:52,537 --> 00:00:53,976
You'd secretly tell me

13
00:00:53,977 --> 00:00:54,976
the whole truth.

14
00:00:55,137 --> 00:00:56,216
Let me cooperate with you.

15
00:00:56,457 --> 00:00:57,496
But you didn't at all.

16
00:00:58,537 --> 00:00:59,976
You played me so badly.

17
00:01:02,097 --> 00:01:03,136
Because I knew

18
00:01:03,937 --> 00:01:05,936
Nanxi must have bribed someone around you.

19
00:01:07,137 --> 00:01:09,936
But I couldn't be sure who betrayed you.

20
00:01:11,937 --> 00:01:12,776
So I had no choice

21
00:01:12,777 --> 00:01:13,976
but to fight alone.

22
00:01:15,457 --> 00:01:16,536
I thought after everything

23
00:01:16,537 --> 00:01:17,536
was resolved,

24
00:01:18,937 --> 00:01:20,256
I'd explain to you.

25
00:01:24,737 --> 00:01:25,896
Are you so sure

26
00:01:26,417 --> 00:01:27,656
that after all this is over,

27
00:01:27,657 --> 00:01:28,416
when you explain,

28
00:01:28,417 --> 00:01:29,416
I'll forgive you?

29
00:01:31,497 --> 00:01:33,576
You'd rather watch me feel lost,

30
00:01:33,577 --> 00:01:34,776
watch me suffer,

31
00:01:35,257 --> 00:01:37,616
watch me get framed by those around me,

32
00:01:38,497 --> 00:01:39,656
and remain indifferent?

33
00:01:40,977 --> 00:01:42,776
Am I really that worthless to you?

34
00:01:42,817 --> 00:01:43,656
Don't misunderstand.

35
00:01:44,057 --> 00:01:45,096
That's not what I meant.

36
00:01:47,217 --> 00:01:48,416
Then what did you mean?

37
00:01:51,537 --> 00:01:52,976
You can be angry.

38
00:01:55,137 --> 00:01:56,136
You can also

39
00:01:57,777 --> 00:01:58,896
punish me,

40
00:02:01,897 --> 00:02:03,696
if it makes you feel better.

41
00:02:11,337 --> 00:02:12,216
Punish?

42
00:02:14,657 --> 00:02:15,536
Punish me.

43
00:02:31,097 --> 00:02:31,816
Zhou Yimo,

44
00:02:32,897 --> 00:02:33,776
what's wrong with you?

45
00:02:39,137 --> 00:02:40,856
When you first entered the Zhou residence,

46
00:02:43,537 --> 00:02:44,856
I told you, I'm willing to be used by you.

47
00:02:45,257 --> 00:02:46,696
Willing to be your pawn.

48
00:02:48,657 --> 00:02:49,856
Please trust me.

49
00:02:50,897 --> 00:02:52,376
That promise still stands.

50
00:02:54,617 --> 00:02:55,416
So

51
00:02:56,537 --> 00:02:57,576
I don't blame you.

52
00:03:13,417 --> 00:03:15,136
Once Nanxi is convicted,

53
00:03:18,137 --> 00:03:20,096
I will truly commit

54
00:03:20,697 --> 00:03:22,216
to our relationship.

55
00:03:26,817 --> 00:03:27,616
You promise?

56
00:03:32,257 --> 00:03:33,056
I promise.

57
00:03:33,817 --> 00:03:34,776
Don't lie to me.

58
00:04:22,937 --> 00:04:24,176
You're finally here.

59
00:04:27,777 --> 00:04:28,696
Director Zhou.

60
00:04:29,457 --> 00:04:30,696
I never expected

61
00:04:31,377 --> 00:04:32,616
that the entire Zhou family

62
00:04:32,697 --> 00:04:34,176
would be manipulated

63
00:04:34,177 --> 00:04:35,656
by a young girl like you.

64
00:04:36,897 --> 00:04:38,616
Actually, I'm aiming for bigger stakes.

65
00:04:39,377 --> 00:04:40,536
I wonder if you

66
00:04:41,257 --> 00:04:42,296
could help me?

67
00:04:46,777 --> 00:04:47,896
Is this simply

68
00:04:47,937 --> 00:04:49,936
because of the so-called evidence

69
00:04:49,937 --> 00:04:51,936
you have against me?

70
00:04:53,657 --> 00:04:54,776
Aren't you afraid

71
00:04:55,937 --> 00:04:57,576
I'm here to silence you?

72
00:05:00,537 --> 00:05:02,576
Director Zhou, you don't actually think

73
00:05:02,937 --> 00:05:04,336
there's only one copy of the evidence of

74
00:05:04,337 --> 00:05:05,736
your opium dealings with Master Zhou

75
00:05:06,217 --> 00:05:07,256
all these years

76
00:05:08,737 --> 00:05:10,056
in my hands, do you?

77
00:05:12,937 --> 00:05:14,256
Where's the remaining evidence?

78
00:05:15,417 --> 00:05:16,496
If I tell you,

79
00:05:17,377 --> 00:05:18,936
I won't survive tonight.

80
00:05:20,137 --> 00:05:21,056
Director Zhou,

81
00:05:21,057 --> 00:05:24,656
you really underestimated me, didn't you?

82
00:05:27,297 --> 00:05:28,296
Then what do you want?

83
00:05:28,897 --> 00:05:30,936
I've made a deal with people outside.

84
00:05:31,657 --> 00:05:32,816
If I die,

85
00:05:33,497 --> 00:05:35,376
all your criminal evidence

86
00:05:35,657 --> 00:05:37,136
will be made public.

87
00:05:38,297 --> 00:05:40,936
You have power, status, a family.

88
00:05:41,817 --> 00:05:42,936
If I die,

89
00:05:43,577 --> 00:05:44,536
those outside

90
00:05:45,177 --> 00:05:46,696
won't hold back anymore.

91
00:05:49,177 --> 00:05:50,056
Protecting me

92
00:05:50,457 --> 00:05:51,616
is protecting you.

93
00:05:52,097 --> 00:05:52,976
Director Zhou,

94
00:05:54,257 --> 00:05:55,176
the choice is yours.

95
00:05:58,657 --> 00:05:59,616
Sorry, Mrs. Zhou.

96
00:05:59,897 --> 00:06:00,616
No, Ms. Ye.

97
00:06:01,297 --> 00:06:02,536
I'm just trying to get by.

98
00:06:02,777 --> 00:06:03,776
Don't come after me.

99
00:06:03,897 --> 00:06:04,696
Go find Director Zhou.

100
00:06:15,657 --> 00:06:16,296
Young Master Zhou.

101
00:06:16,657 --> 00:06:17,616
This is a police station.

102
00:06:17,937 --> 00:06:18,776
You're obstructing justice.

103
00:06:18,817 --> 00:06:20,616
You're the one obstructing justice.

104
00:06:20,977 --> 00:06:21,736
What are you burning?

105
00:06:22,937 --> 00:06:23,656
No comment.

106
00:06:26,817 --> 00:06:27,656
I'll cover you.

107
00:06:27,857 --> 00:06:28,856
Run south.

108
00:06:29,897 --> 00:06:30,736
What about you?

109
00:06:31,297 --> 00:06:33,136
With my status, he won't dare touch me.

110
00:06:33,617 --> 00:06:34,456
Ye Zhiqiu.

111
00:06:35,897 --> 00:06:37,136
Remember why

112
00:06:37,137 --> 00:06:38,296
you came this far.

113
00:06:38,897 --> 00:06:40,376
Protect the evidence at all costs.

114
00:06:41,297 --> 00:06:41,936
Go!

115
00:06:42,817 --> 00:06:43,616
Mr. Zhou.

116
00:06:43,857 --> 00:06:44,616
It's so late.

117
00:06:44,617 --> 00:06:45,816
Where are you heading?

118
00:06:49,577 --> 00:06:50,376
Uncle.

119
00:06:50,657 --> 00:06:51,736
What crime have I committed?

120
00:06:52,297 --> 00:06:54,136
Everyone's pointing guns at me.

121
00:06:55,817 --> 00:06:57,056
Leave it.

122
00:07:02,337 --> 00:07:04,416
What you want is in my hands.

123
00:07:04,697 --> 00:07:05,536
Put down your guns.

124
00:07:06,257 --> 00:07:07,136
Put them down!

125
00:07:09,817 --> 00:07:10,616
Ye Zhiqiu.

126
00:07:10,697 --> 00:07:11,456
What good is she

127
00:07:11,497 --> 00:07:12,536
to the Zhou family?

128
00:07:13,257 --> 00:07:13,896
For her,

129
00:07:13,937 --> 00:07:15,456
you'd sacrifice me?

130
00:07:15,457 --> 00:07:16,296
Uncle.

131
00:07:17,137 --> 00:07:18,296
I'm from the He family.

132
00:07:26,777 --> 00:07:28,216
Four years, Ms. Ye.

133
00:07:28,577 --> 00:07:30,536
You haven't changed a bit.

134
00:07:33,257 --> 00:07:33,976
Yes.

135
00:07:34,697 --> 00:07:35,656
Four years.

136
00:07:36,537 --> 00:07:37,496
Four years ago, you burned

137
00:07:37,497 --> 00:07:38,896
my sister's autopsy report.

138
00:07:39,177 --> 00:07:40,416
Let her die in vain.

139
00:07:40,777 --> 00:07:42,376
Now the truth will come out.

140
00:07:42,377 --> 00:07:43,576
Justice will be served.

141
00:07:43,817 --> 00:07:45,056
Isn't this the outcome

142
00:07:45,057 --> 00:07:46,496
you cops hope for?

143
00:07:48,737 --> 00:07:50,496
I only want power and wealth.

144
00:07:50,817 --> 00:07:52,816
What does this have to do with me?

145
00:07:55,857 --> 00:07:56,616
I can

146
00:07:57,257 --> 00:07:58,376
give you anything.

147
00:08:03,777 --> 00:08:05,496
And you were once my subordinate.

148
00:08:06,297 --> 00:08:07,536
So ungrateful.

149
00:08:08,057 --> 00:08:10,576
Do you think you can bully Ms. Ye?

150
00:08:10,897 --> 00:08:11,376
No,

151
00:08:11,377 --> 00:08:12,056
no, bro.

152
00:08:12,257 --> 00:08:13,336
Bro, let me explain.

153
00:08:13,377 --> 00:08:15,416
Zhou Quan threatened my family's lives.

154
00:08:16,137 --> 00:08:17,176
I had no choice.

155
00:08:17,497 --> 00:08:18,816
You still remember me, huh?

156
00:08:20,137 --> 00:08:20,776
Good.

157
00:08:23,657 --> 00:08:24,656
Since we're friends,

158
00:08:24,897 --> 00:08:26,296
your family's safety

159
00:08:26,577 --> 00:08:27,376
is my responsibility.

160
00:08:28,417 --> 00:08:29,056
Remember:

161
00:08:29,417 --> 00:08:30,616
from now on, Ms. Ye's affairs

162
00:08:30,657 --> 00:08:31,656
are my affairs.

163
00:08:32,137 --> 00:08:32,696
Got it?

164
00:08:33,697 --> 00:08:34,336
Got it.

165
00:08:35,137 --> 00:08:35,696
Understood.

166
00:08:36,377 --> 00:08:37,096
Get in.

167
00:08:44,857 --> 00:08:45,536
Ms. Ye,

168
00:08:47,177 --> 00:08:48,336
you're truly fearless.

169
00:08:50,297 --> 00:08:52,336
You can come and go from the police station freely.

170
00:08:52,617 --> 00:08:54,176
Seems my presence here is unnecessary.

171
00:08:54,377 --> 00:08:55,096
It's needed.

172
00:08:58,417 --> 00:08:59,416
Can you help me?

173
00:09:01,417 --> 00:09:02,176
Help with what?

174
00:09:02,537 --> 00:09:03,416
Could you...

175
00:09:05,497 --> 00:09:06,336
go in

176
00:09:07,217 --> 00:09:08,816
and rescue Zhou Yimo?

177
00:09:10,897 --> 00:09:11,656
You want me

178
00:09:12,057 --> 00:09:12,696
to go in

179
00:09:13,057 --> 00:09:13,776
and save him?

180
00:09:14,537 --> 00:09:15,296
Who do you think I am?

181
00:09:17,537 --> 00:09:18,176
Xiaoman,

182
00:09:19,297 --> 00:09:20,296
do you think

183
00:09:20,937 --> 00:09:21,376
I can be

184
00:09:21,537 --> 00:09:22,896
easily manipulated by you?

185
00:09:24,657 --> 00:09:25,976
I'm not joking.

186
00:09:28,537 --> 00:09:29,096
Xiaoman,

187
00:09:29,777 --> 00:09:30,616
I came today

188
00:09:31,737 --> 00:09:32,416
because Zhou Yimo

189
00:09:32,417 --> 00:09:33,536
asked me to pick you up.

190
00:09:35,537 --> 00:09:36,336
Don't worry.

191
00:09:37,337 --> 00:09:38,256
He'll be fine.

192
00:09:41,217 --> 00:09:42,856
You planned this together all along?

193
00:09:44,617 --> 00:09:45,536
Cooperate?

194
00:09:46,097 --> 00:09:47,296
Why would I cooperate with him?

195
00:09:49,657 --> 00:09:51,056
I only agreed

196
00:09:52,297 --> 00:09:53,536
because of your safety.

197
00:09:56,057 --> 00:09:56,856
Let's go.

198
00:10:00,977 --> 00:10:02,176
You must save him.

199
00:10:03,737 --> 00:10:04,416
Xiaoman,

200
00:10:05,337 --> 00:10:06,096
everything

201
00:10:06,457 --> 00:10:07,696
has been arranged.

202
00:10:08,177 --> 00:10:09,536
I have people outside the station.

203
00:10:10,217 --> 00:10:11,296
Just relax.

204
00:10:12,057 --> 00:10:13,216
The most important thing now

205
00:10:13,537 --> 00:10:15,296
is to keep the evidence safe.

206
00:10:19,617 --> 00:10:20,296
Xiaoman,

207
00:10:22,817 --> 00:10:23,816
everything I've done

208
00:10:25,657 --> 00:10:26,576
is for you.

209
00:10:32,657 --> 00:10:34,776
[Zhou's residence]

210
00:10:36,657 --> 00:10:38,096
Why are you back at his place?

211
00:10:44,857 --> 00:10:45,776
Leave.

212
00:10:56,097 --> 00:10:57,176
So afraid of me?

213
00:11:02,057 --> 00:11:02,896
Or...

214
00:11:03,417 --> 00:11:04,816
afraid I'll take your evidence?

215
00:11:19,857 --> 00:11:20,656
Lieutenant Yu,

216
00:11:21,337 --> 00:11:22,696
thank you for earlier.

217
00:11:24,977 --> 00:11:26,176
I still hope someday

218
00:11:27,057 --> 00:11:28,696
you'll call me Shi'an.

219
00:11:32,617 --> 00:11:33,656
Saving your life

220
00:11:34,057 --> 00:11:36,216
deserves some reward, right?

221
00:11:36,297 --> 00:11:37,056
Don't you think?

222
00:11:37,897 --> 00:11:38,536
Fine.

223
00:11:40,417 --> 00:11:41,296
Shi'an.

224
00:12:34,177 --> 00:12:35,176
Shi'an.

225
00:12:35,657 --> 00:12:37,176
Shi'an.

226
00:12:40,657 --> 00:12:41,776
Once we arrive,

227
00:12:42,057 --> 00:12:43,256
remember to examine the evidence.

228
00:12:44,137 --> 00:12:46,056
If the handwriting is severely damaged by fire,

229
00:12:46,537 --> 00:12:48,416
the other party may deny writing it.

230
00:12:58,297 --> 00:12:59,056
I'm back.

231
00:13:01,217 --> 00:13:01,976
How are you?

232
00:13:04,337 --> 00:13:05,176
I'm fine.

233
00:13:05,417 --> 00:13:06,296
Silly.

234
00:13:06,657 --> 00:13:07,736
Didn't I tell you?

235
00:13:08,177 --> 00:13:09,456
I have people inside the police station.

236
00:13:09,737 --> 00:13:10,536
And outside,

237
00:13:10,537 --> 00:13:12,096
Yu Shi'an has military forces deployed.

238
00:13:13,617 --> 00:13:14,976
What can Zhou Quan do to me?

239
00:13:18,177 --> 00:13:20,976
Did Yu Shi'an give you any trouble?

240
00:13:22,057 --> 00:13:23,336
Since he agreed to help you,

241
00:13:23,777 --> 00:13:24,936
of course he didn't trouble me.

242
00:13:28,537 --> 00:13:29,896
If I weren't absolutely certain,

243
00:13:31,057 --> 00:13:32,456
I wouldn't have asked him for help.

244
00:13:35,417 --> 00:13:36,616
I'm just glad you're back safely.

245
00:13:40,857 --> 00:13:41,696
Where's the evidence?

246
00:13:45,137 --> 00:13:46,776
The evidence was destroyed beyond recognition.

247
00:13:57,977 --> 00:13:58,816
Your Honor,

248
00:13:59,297 --> 00:14:00,456
Through Ms. Ye Zhiqiu's

249
00:14:00,457 --> 00:14:01,656
year-long undercover investigation,

250
00:14:01,657 --> 00:14:03,056
the full sequence of Ye Chuxue's death

251
00:14:03,257 --> 00:14:04,336
on New Year's Eve three years ago

252
00:14:04,337 --> 00:14:06,736
has been reconstructed.

253
00:14:10,537 --> 00:14:11,496
On the night of the incident,

254
00:14:11,817 --> 00:14:12,976
Steward Xu Hansheng

255
00:14:13,297 --> 00:14:14,056
received a letter of invitation

256
00:14:14,057 --> 00:14:15,616
from Ye Chuxue,

257
00:14:15,977 --> 00:14:18,536
asking him to meet her by the pond in the backyard.

258
00:14:18,937 --> 00:14:20,656
However, according to multiple sources of evidence,

259
00:14:20,697 --> 00:14:21,936
at this time, Ye Chuxue

260
00:14:21,937 --> 00:14:23,376
had just escaped from Zhou Yichen's

261
00:14:23,377 --> 00:14:24,816
private residence,

262
00:14:24,977 --> 00:14:26,096
covered in injuries,

263
00:14:26,377 --> 00:14:27,856
and her face was covered in scratches.

264
00:14:28,177 --> 00:14:29,536
This matches the testimonies given before death

265
00:14:29,617 --> 00:14:31,896
by Zhou Yichen and Steward Xu Hansheng,

266
00:14:32,257 --> 00:14:32,936
as well as

267
00:14:32,937 --> 00:14:35,176
her own autopsy report.

268
00:15:09,537 --> 00:15:10,256
Chuxue,

269
00:15:10,577 --> 00:15:12,056
Steward Xu asked you to go to the backyard.

270
00:15:14,257 --> 00:15:14,976
I...

271
00:15:15,457 --> 00:15:16,536
I've already gone to bed.

272
00:15:16,737 --> 00:15:18,536
I'm not feeling well. Can it wait until tomorrow?

273
00:15:18,977 --> 00:15:19,696
No.

274
00:15:19,937 --> 00:15:21,576
The Steward seemed very angry.

275
00:15:21,977 --> 00:15:22,736
How about this,

276
00:15:23,137 --> 00:15:24,336
I'll go with you, okay?

277
00:15:24,537 --> 00:15:25,176
No.

278
00:15:27,737 --> 00:15:28,816
I'll go alone.

279
00:15:29,497 --> 00:15:30,576
Don't come with me.

280
00:15:55,977 --> 00:15:57,216
Nanxi?
